      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <em>PZO1110</em></p>\r\n<p>If you drink a vial of antitoxin, you get a +5 <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Bonus-Alchemical-\">alchemical bonus</a> on <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Fortitude\">Fortitude</a> <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Saving-Throws\">saving throws</a> against <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions#TOC-Poison\">poison</a> for 1 hour.</p>\r\n<p class=\"header\">Alchemical Power Component</p>\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <em>PZO9410</em></p>\r\n<p>Like antiplague, antitoxin can augment certain <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Conjuration-Healing\">healing</a> spells.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a class=\"spell\" href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/n/neutralize-poison\">Neutralize Poison</a> (M): Add +2 on your <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic#TOC-Caster-Level\">caster level</a> check to neutralize poison on a target creature. Antitoxin has no effect when you cast the spell on an object.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n"
